{
  "stem": "14613.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I, I really could not say too much about it, whether he had a political affiliation or not.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It is something that, at that point in my life, before the war, we really did not discuss so much.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] My father, I mean-- he worked quite hard, I think.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, and we didn't have, maybe, so much open lines of communication as you have here right now.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's a big difference.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Although, when we're talking about my father and my mother, there was a big difference between them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The, the, the father would always-- and my sister would always complain that he sticks always with the boys because he would allow us-- or give us a lot of things which the girls would not get.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, when we were on-- in the summer vacation, he would buy for us all sporting equipment.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Our, our villa in-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] was a meeting place, in a way, for all the kids around the neighborhood because we had a very big-- it was not a yard.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was a big field.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So that we had there a place to play soccer, volleyball, basketball.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my father liked to give it to us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And also, I remember when he used to come for the weekend, he, he used to take us-- means the boys-- horseback riding, rather than having it, which you may have here, together with the girls.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And at that time, my mother did not participate these-- in any sports activities or horseback riding.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That goes without saying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No-- my, my mother related to me in a way like, maybe, we always talk about our mothers, that they are with us.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was with us all the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
